section.def:
Board
                (董事局) means the Board of the Ocean Park
            Corporation established by section 7(1);

Corporation
                (海洋公園公司) means the Ocean Park Corporation
            established by section 3(1);

Fund
                (基金) means the Ocean Park Trust Fund established
            by section 30(1);

paragraph.content:
all movable or immovable property that, immediately before that
                    commencement, was vested in the company shall vest in the Corporation on the
                    same terms and conditions on which it was so vested in the company;

subparagraph.content:
for the purposes of recreation, education or conservation;
                            (Replaced 26 of 2021 s.
                            5)

paragraph.content:
apply for and receive sponsorships, receive gifts, whether on trust or
                otherwise, and act as trustee of moneys or other property vested in it on
                trust;

erect, provide, equip, maintain, alter, remove, demolish, replace, enlarge,
                improve and keep in repair its buildings, premises, furniture and
                equipment;
